data.description: Seize this exceptional opportunity to own a charming 3-bedroom, 3-bathroom home in the heart of Spanish Town. Upon approaching the house, you'll be captivated by the expansive front yard, ripe with potential for beautiful landscaping, and a warm, inviting front porch. Step inside your future home to discover the original hardwood floors, abundant natural light, and an elegant formal dining room. To your left, you'll find a generously sized bedroom at the front of the house, complete with its own full bathroom. Additionally, there's another bedroom conveniently situated near the kitchen, also with its own full bathroom. You'll be delighted to find clawfoot tubs in two of the three bathrooms. At the rear of the house, a spacious bonus area awaits, offering access to the third bathroom, the third bedroom, a utility room, and a back porch. Enjoy your backyard oasis from the comfort of your porch and make the most of the additional storage space. Don't miss out on this exceptional opportunity. Schedule a tour of your future home today! The refrigerator, washer, and dryer are included, and it's worth noting that the property did not flood in 2016!
